"2  oranges, thinly sliced","2  apples, cored and thinly sliced","2  bottles (750 ml. each) red wine","1/2 cup brandy","1/2 cup triple sec or Cointreau","1 cup pomegranate juice","1/4 cup simple syrup","2 tablespoons pomegranate molasses* (optional)","2  to 4 cups sparkling water, at room temperature","1  2-lb. chunk of dry ice*"